Package: simATAC
Type: Package
Date: 2020-07-27
Title: This package is a single-cell ATAC sequencing simulator
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Zeinab Navidi Ghaziani
Maintainer: Zeinab Navidi Ghaziani <zeinab.navidighaziani@uhnresearch.ca>
Description: This package provides a set of functions to simulate single-cell ATAC-seq
             count matrix from real single-cell samples. simATAC first estimates the 
             parameters of statistical models fitted to the library size, bin count mean, 
             and non-zero cell proportion parameters. simATAC generates the final synthetic 
             counts using the estimated models.
